# PCA

```python
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn import decomposition
import seaborn as sns

data = pd.read_csv('./HGF-Andrea/HGFfinal.merge.csv', low_memory=False)

#subsetting balance sheet final parameters

data=data[['Shareholders.funds.th.EUR.2010',
           'P.L.for.period...Net.income..th.EUR.2010',
           'Current.liabilities.th.EUR.2010',
           'Non.current.liabilities.th.EUR.2010',
           'Total.assets.th.EUR.2010',
           'P.L.after.tax.th.EUR.2010',
           'Cash.flow.th.EUR.2010',
           'HGF'
            ]]
#fill na's with 0s
data=data.fillna(0)

# PCA
pca = decomposition.PCA(n_components=4)
pc = pca.fit_transform(data.drop('HGF',axis=1))
# label PCs
pcNames = ['PC1','PC2','PC3','PC4']
pc_df = pd.DataFrame(data = pc , columns = pcNames)
# re-add labels
pc_df['HGF']=data['HGF']

# plot



lm=sns.lmplot( x="PC1", y="PC2",
  data=pc_df, 
  fit_reg=False, 
  height=10,
  hue='HGF', 
  palette="Set2",              
  legend=True,
  scatter_kws={"s": 10, 'alpha':.5}) # specify the point size

axes = lm.axes

# zoom
axes[0,0].set_ylim(-2e4,2e4)
axes[0,0].set_xlim(-10000,3e4)
axes[0,0].axhline(0, ls=':')
axes[0,0].axvline(0, ls=':')

sns.set_style("darkgrid", {"axes.facecolor": ".9"})
```
